   ldap-3.3 package</link>, <link xlink:href="&url.ldap.netscape.sdk;"> Netscape
   Directory SDK 3.0</link> or <link xlink:href="&url.ldap.openldap.source;">
   OpenLDAP</link> to compile PHP with LDAP support.
